version_description:
- Remove Background of Images with Artificial Intelligence
- Sign In ( with Apple, Google and Facebook ).
- Add In-App Purchases to Remove Ads.
- iCloud Sync for Backup and Restore Data.
- Support Siri Shortcuts For ( Create New Package - Show Packages ...etc)
- Support English and Arabic Language
- Support Dark Mode
- The ability to report a bug in app
- Add some improvements and fix some problems
